\v 7 Kodwa uNkulunkulu uzabatshoka ngomtshoko masinyane; bazalinyazwa\x + Hlab. 58.7. 64.7. Jer. 9.3. Hlab. 7.12.\x*.
\v 8 Njalo bazakwenza olwabo ulimi luwele phezu kwabo\x + Zaga 18.7.\x*; bonke\x + Hlab. 31.11.\x* abababonayo\x + Hlab. 40.3. 52.6.\x* bazabaleka\x + Jer. 48.27.\x*.
\v 9 Labo bonke abantu bazakwesaba\x + Hlab. 40.3. 52.6.\x*, batshumayele isenzo sikaNkulunkulu\x + Jer. 50.28. 51.10.\x*, baqedisise umsebenzi wakhe\x + Jobe 34.27. Hlab. 106.7. 119.99.\x*.
